### gender
p<-ggplot(student.info,aes(your.gender))+geom_bar()+xlab('gender')
plot(p)

### university
p<-ggplot(student.info,aes(your.univ))+geom_bar()+xlab('university')
plot(p)

### university x gender
p<-ggplot(student.info,aes(your.univ,fill=factor(your.gender)))+geom_bar()+xlab('university')
plot(p)

### university x degree
p<-ggplot(student.info,aes(your.univ,fill=factor(your.degree)))+geom_bar()+xlab('university')
plot(p)

### degree
p<-ggplot(student.info,aes(your.degree))+geom_bar()+xlab('degree')
plot(p)

### degree x gender
p<-ggplot(student.info,aes(your.degree,fill=factor(your.gender)))+geom_bar()+xlab('degree')
plot(p)

### school
pdata <- student.info %>% mutate(your.school=tolower(your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('business',your.school),'business',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('lebow',your.school),'business',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('engineering',your.school),'engineering',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('seas',your.school),'engineering',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('science',your.school),'science',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('education',your.school),'education',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('design',your.school),'design',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('law',your.school),'law',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('medicine',your.school),'medicine',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('social policy',your.school),'social policy',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('economics',your.school),'economics',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('english',your.school),'english',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('传播学院',your.school),'communication',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('communication',your.school),'communication',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('sas',your.school),'science',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('gse',your.school),'education',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('sp2',your.school),'social policy',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('mse',your.school),'engineering',your.school)) %>%
mutate(your.school=ifelse(grepl('lps',your.school),'science',your.school)) 

p<- pdata %>% ggplot(aes(your.school))+geom_bar()+xlab('major') + coord_flip()
plot(p)

p <- pdata %>% ggplot(aes(your.school,fill=your.gender))+geom_bar()+xlab('major') + coord_flip()
plot(p)

p <- pdata %>% ggplot(aes(your.school,fill=your.degree))+geom_bar()+xlab('major') + coord_flip()
plot(p)

p <- pdata %>% ggplot(aes(your.school,fill=your.univ))+geom_bar()+xlab('major') + coord_flip()
plot(p)
